      "x": 610,
      "y": 592,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 90,
      "text": "• Employee ID = auto-generated\n• Probation = Hire + 119 days\n• Rehire: Original Start Date preserved\n• Seniority Start Date = rehire date\n• OK to Rehire = No → blacklist\n• Events pre-delivered (relabel only)",
