    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "oe_sen_t",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 5700,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "TTT covers 1 scenario only (Rehire reset). BRD adds 10 scenarios across 6 workflows:\n#86 CRC/CPN counting rules + NON-CNEXT Dummy Assignment  |  #87 Branch size rules (CPN)\n#88 Year In Position event-based reset  |  #94 Override fields (6 custom dates)  |  #102 Re-Hire override\n#103 Promotion/PT→FT always continuous  |  #110 Transfer retain code + continuous  |  #117 Auto-pass 119d",
      "originalText": "TTT covers 1 scenario only (Rehire reset). BRD adds 10 scenarios across 6 workflows:\n#86 CRC/CPN counting rules + NON-CNEXT Dummy Assignment  |  #87 Branch size rules (CPN)\n#88 Year In Position event-based reset  |  #94 Override fields (6 custom dates)  |  #102 Re-Hire override\n#103 Promotion/PT→FT always continuous  |  #110 Transfer retain code + continuous  |  #117 Auto-pass 119d",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
